          'help_text' => 'Within your chosen <a target=\'_blank\' href=\'https://iatistandard.org/en/iati-standard/203/codelists/GeographicVocabulary/\'>administrative boundary list</a>, you can provide a number to define a subdivision within a hierarchical system of administrative areas.',
